{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Defend Your Homeland from Pollution in this Garbage Tower Defense Strategy Game!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A hostile nation is launching trash-filled balloons, threatening to overwhelm your homeland with pollution. Fight back, build powerful turrets, and send the trash back to where it came from!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build and Upgrade Turrets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start by manually aiming turrets to shoot down incoming trash then<strong> </strong>automate them. Experiment with a variety of turret types and upgrades to optimize your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/Upgrades.gif?t=1736775070\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategic Base Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your capabilities by constructing buildings that send trash and other surprises back to the enemy. Balance your economy between offense and defense carefully.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/Building_2.gif?t=1736775070\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dynamic Enemy Challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore different types of enemies, learn about their traits and weaknesses, and try to break through your opponent's defenses. Over time, enemies will become stronger and more cunning, challenging the limits of your strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/FarmingAndMining_7.gif?t=1736775070\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Survival Strategy meets Leaderboards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your villagers alive by building farms and managing resources.\u00a0 They clean trash and man your turrets.\u00a0 Can you survive and top the leaderboard?</p><p class=\"bb_p